snippet: The National Guard stormed a suspected militant hide-out after a daylong standoff, killing seven militants, including a suspect in a political assassination last year, the interior minister said.
abstract: National Guard storms suspected militant hideout in Tunis, killing seven militants, including Kamel Gadhgadhi, suspect in a 2013 political assassination.
lead_paragraph: The National Guard stormed a suspected militant hide-out after a daylong standoff, killing seven militants, including a suspect in a political assassination last year, the interior minister said.
